  "original_title": "\u0b8a\u0bb0\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b86\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc7\u0baa\u0ba3\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Bar Association strongly objected to the curfew",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lankan Bar Association has strongly objected to the imposition of curfew in some parts of the Upper Province.",
        "The Sri Lankan Bar Association has stated that there is no provision in the Police Act to issue such a curfew and said it would like to ask the Inspector General of Police on what basis he issued the order.",
        "The Sri Lankan Bar Association said that curfew has been enacted to stifle freedom of expression and freedom of dissent."
      ],
